Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Anak keluarga kekaisaran\Nkerap wafat sebelum waktunya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Artinya, banyak yang wafat muda.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:07:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Secara resmi, kematiannya\Ndianggap karena wabah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Namun, ada juga yang bilang mati\Ndiracun karena perebutan kekuasaan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Yang jelas, itu nyawa\Npewaris yang berharga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sebelum mencapai usia dewasa,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pangeran dilarang terjun\Nke medan perang tanpa titah Kaisar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah 12 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Punya pengalaman sebelum memasuki\Nwilayah kekuasaan bisa menjaga martabatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apabila Yang Mulia mentitahkan,\Naku siap kapan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau punya pedang iblis.\NKurasa itu bukan hal sulit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan pertempuran pertama Kanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa tiba-tiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, berengsek!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar bocah tengik!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyusahkan kami saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Percuma saja kabur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa pun... tolong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Woi, kemari!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Jangan!\N- Hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Jangan ikut campur\Nyang bukan urusanmu, Bocah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Legalitasnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Legalitasnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu akta-aktanya?\NToko kalian jenisnya apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jawab.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurut hukum kekaisaran,\Nperdagangan manusia tanpa legalitas
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah kejahatan berat, kalian tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berisik, bocah tengik!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sikat habis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pergerakannya seperti ahli pedang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak bangsawan mana, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka pedagang budak ilegal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka bilang kami bisa\Nmenghasilkan banyak uang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cukup sampai situ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suatu kehormatan bisa bertemu Anda,\NYang Mulia Pangeran Arif.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya mencari nafkah dengan\Nmemperdagangkan anak-anak ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal nama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih baik tidak saya sampaikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alasannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu karena saya adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pesuruh Yang Mulia\NPangeran Pertama Gilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran Pertama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Rupanya dia sudah tahu siapa aku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dengan Kanda Gilbert sebagai pelindungnya,\Ndia mengancamku untuk tak ikut campur.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya tak ingin memperbesar perkara ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, anggap saja Anda\Ntidak melihat hal ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Kanda kenal pria ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak kenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kanda Henry berkata tidak mengenalmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja demikian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang seperti saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lancang sekali kau mengaku\Nsebagai pesuruh Pangeran Pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kau bisa menipu orang lain,\Naku dan Kandaku takkan tertipu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Jadi, dia palsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, mereka berdua...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beliau adalah Pangeran Arif\Nyang jadi penjamin diva Alichey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti mereka pemimpin sungguhan?\NLalu yang satunya itu palsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangkap mereka dan bawa\Nke mansion Pangeran Pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan mereka dengan tuduhan "orang\Nyang mengaku pesuruh Kanda Gilbert."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak-anak itu antar ke mansionku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti akan kudengar penjelasannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja bagus, Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menanganinya dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah berhasil teratasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika mereka memang pesuruh Kanda Gilbert,\Ntak mungkin langsung kueksekusi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau tadi mereka dibiarkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}maka kita akan dianggap mengabaikan\Npraktik perdagangan budak ilegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi kita anggap mereka pesuruh palsu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan biarkan Kanda yang menanganinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Caramu selalu melebihi dugaanku. Hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dimengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa, Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari Pangeran Pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepatnya, ada utusan dari Kanda Gilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, apa katanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hebat bisa menangkap mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah orang-orang lancang diinterogasi,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ternyata mereka memang berdagang\Ndengan membawa namaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rencananya, besok akan\Nkubawa mereka ke pengadilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun saat lengah,\Nmereka malah bunuh diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh. Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ya ampun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Padahal manusia adalah harta.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pastilah perkataan sama\Njuga terlintas di benak Kanda.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}"Memutus ekor cicak."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perdagangan budak ilegal itu memang\Ndijalankan atas titah Kanda Gilbert, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak dulu, dia sibuk mengurus\Ntoko dan membeli tanah feodal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia terobsesi hal-hal konyol.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kanda Gilbert memang\Npangeran pertama, tapi dia anak selir.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak dapat mewarisi takhta.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah sebagai pelampiasan kekecewaan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau mencari pengganti takhta\Nyang tidak bisa diwarisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik perdagangan atau tanah feodal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua hanya pengganti, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah tahu sejauh itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau memang mengagumkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cukup berpikir lebih dalam,\Nhal itu bisa diketahui.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya tidak begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski ini topik yang membuat muak,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku sedikit terhibur berkatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua sudah kuurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian takkan dijual lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian sudah bebas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa ini... maksudnya begitu?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian punya tempat tujuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya dijual sebagai pengganti\Nbiaya benih padi tahun ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya dijual untuk biaya pemakaman\Nibu sekaligus mengurangi tanggungan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah saya suka berjudi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sudah kuduga, mereka tak punya\Ntempat pulang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:14:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kalau orang tuanya begitu,\Nmereka pasti dijual lagi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dylan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ambil alih mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sediakan tempat tidur\Ndan pekerjaan yang layak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, beri pendidikan\Nbagi mereka yang mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuai titah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti biasanya, benar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda akan membeli kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan membeli.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, jika kalian mau pergi,\Npergilah kapan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya saja,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak memaafkan pengkhianat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa terlalu rumit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersyukurlah atas kemurahan hati Pangeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian hanya perlu mengabdi\Ndengan segenap ketulusan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Segera sampaikan terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Manusia adalah harta, ya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda memanggil saya, Tuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terkait penanganan hadiah ulang tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah selesai ditangani tanpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cukup soal laporannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah paham tanpa bertanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Evelyn, kubawakan ini untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Surat keputusan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadilah penguasa sebidang tanah\Ndi wilayah Almeria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penguasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan begini,\Nkau adalah pejabat resmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sa-Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Penguasa wilayah adalah jabatan\Nyang disebut "wakil pangeran" oleh rakyat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Bagi pelayan,\Nitu kenaikan status yang drastis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Wilayah kekuasaan pemberian\NKaisar sangat luas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tentu tidak bisa dikelola satu orang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Maka, para penguasa wilayah ditempatkan\Nsebagai perwakilan pangeran.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah lama memperhatikanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yang paling cerdas\Ndi antara para pelayan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mubazir kalau kau hanya\Nmenangani urusan mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah pikirku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Na-Namun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal itu, saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada bertugas di luar\Nuntuk naik jabatan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saya lebih ingin mengabdi pada Tuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, kau bisa berkembang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kiprahmu bagus sebagai penguasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku yang mengutusmu akan\Ndianggap tepat menilai orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Evelyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pergilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bekerjalah demiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demi Tuan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba-Baik. Saya mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:16:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak diragukan lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda sangat berbeda dibanding\NPangeran Pertama dalam memperlakukan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shirley.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hal seperti itu tak pantas diucapkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba-Baik. Saya mohon maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beliau memang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah mendengarnya, Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau telah menjaga kehormatan Gilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu hanya kebetulan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya hanya menangkap pelanggar hukum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kanda sendiri yang melaporkannya, ya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Cerdas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ini membuatnya tampak tak bersalah,\Ndibanding menutupi secara berlebihan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata ada juga\Norang-orang yang lancang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kejahatan apa yang berlaku\Npada pedagang budak ilegal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelaku utama perdagangan manusia\Nilegal dihukum potong lengan dominan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:18:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sisanya dihukum wajib militer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar demikian, Kanselir Utama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuai perkataan Yang Mulia Pangeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh iya. Kau tidak terluka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar bandit itu kalut\Ndan menyerangmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untungnya, saya mampu melawan balik.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, karena itu Noah,\Ntidak perlu diragukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau itu aku,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin akan telanjur dihajar saat bimbang\Nmau memperkenalkan diri atau tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu namanya kejahatan\Npenghinaan terhadap Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hukumannya adalah pidana mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam hukum kekaisaran,\Npihak yang tidak tahu identitas Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yakni apabila Yang Mulia menyamar\Natau belum memperkenalkan diri,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}maka kejahatan penghinaan\Ntidak dapat diterapkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya dianggap tindak kekerasan biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa aku berlebihan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Hal sopan atau tidak sopan terhadap\NKaisar adalah masalah sensitif.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kalau hanya sekadar perumpamaan,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}mungkin tidak perlu dipermasalahkan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku memang menyampaikan\Npendapat yang benar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Namun menjatuhkan wibawa\NKanselir bukanlah hal baik.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Minta maaf saja, ya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana? Aku yang menang\Ntaruhannya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Mohon maaf atas kekeliruan saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eng... Apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan apa-apa. Aku hanya\Nbertaruh dengan Kanselir Utama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menguji apakah kau\Nmampu bicara hukum secara jujur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Menguji? Untuk apa?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kau sejak dulu\Ntak pandang bulu soal hukum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk berjaga-jaga,\Naku hanya memastikan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wahai Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atas nama Kaisar,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku mengangkat Noah Ararat\Nsebagai Menteri Hukum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah Pangeran Keempat, sekarang muncul\NPangeran selanjutnya yang jadi menteri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran dan Menteri Hukum Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hidup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hidup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hidup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Padahal aku menjawab seperti biasanya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tapi aku diangkat sebagai Menteri Hukum.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa ini hanya perasaanku saja?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Atau di balik keputusan ini ada hal lain?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Mimpi singkat yang masih tak sampai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kutakut akan peluh\NYang tak kunjung sembuh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diva terpopuler di kekaisaran\Nmemang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suaranya merdu sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hatiku seakan dimurnikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Siluet terpantul di tepi jendela{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Benar juga. Tidak pantas\Nmemikirkan itu sekarang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kenanganku bersamamu\Nperlahan memudar{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Diterangi sinar rembulan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enak, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kulihat dirimu bersinar\NBagai bintang nun jauh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Walau musim berganti, waktu berlalu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Rasaku padamu tidak{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Harapku agar sajak cinta abadi ini\NKian sampai padamu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Walau kutahu kan terwujud\NAku tetap memimpikannya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Air mataku mengering{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Pemandangan mengabur\NDi seberang keabadian{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Walau aku terlepas bayang-bayangmu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baginda, bagaimana soal\Nkesalahan informasi itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:22:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Hatiku kan terpaut di sisimu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penanganannya kuserahkan padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuai titah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya waktu tidak\Nmau menunggu lebih lama.
